  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Blend-Point Editor: X–axis Controls</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">BLEND-POINT EDITOR :</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> &#160;</text><text styleclass="Separator-Header" translate="true"> X-axis Values </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">&#32;</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">When you edit the X-axis value of a </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Blend-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> you do NOT change the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Motion-Width</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">, but you do edit the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment-Width</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Previous-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> and the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Separator-Header" style="font-size:12pt;" translate="true"> X-axis Values </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="AStandard" rowcount="2" colcount="1" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; cell-border-width:0px; border-style:none;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MT-BPE-X-axisControls.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Parameter"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Motion Start</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">&#32;</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#993300; border-style:solid;">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Move the entire (all of the) motion relative to the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Master-Machine-Angle" styleclass="Interface" translate="true">Master Machine Angle</link></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">The </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Motion-Width" styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Motion-Width</link><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> does not change.</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">X-axis </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="border-width:0px; border-spacing:0px; border-collapse:collapse; cell-border-width:1px; border-color:#993300; border-style:solid;">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">Move the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">X-axis value</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">active Blend-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> along the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">X-axis</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> - </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">see </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;" translate="true">SPECIAL CASE</text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">and </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;" translate="true">WARNING</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">X-axis values</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> of all other </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Blend-Points</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> do not move - see </text><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">Warning</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">Special Case</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">: </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">X-axis Value</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Blend-Point #1</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">If you attempt to increase the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">X-axis value </text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">of </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Blend-Point #1</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">...you increase the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-SegmentEditor-Segment-Width" styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Segment-Width</link><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Previous-Segment</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> (#1)</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> and decrease the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Segment-Width</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> (see </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;" translate="true">WARNING</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">).</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">If you attempt to decrease the X-axis value of </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Blend-Point #1</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">...you increase the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Segment-Width</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true"> (#1) </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">and decrease the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Segment-Width</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Previous-Segment</text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">(see </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" style="font-style:normal; color:#ff0000;" translate="true">WARNING</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">).</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text"><anchor id="BPE-Warning-Xaxis" styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;"><keywords><keyword translate="true">Blend-Point Editor:<keyword translate="true">WARNING: Bumping Segment-Wdith</keyword></keyword></keywords></anchor><text styleclass="VariableName" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">WARNING</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">: </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Bumping Blend-Points !</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="PopupTable2" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">If you edit the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">X-axis value</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> of the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Active Blend-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> such that it </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="true">bumps</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> into an adjacent </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Blend-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">, then the adjacent</text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">Blend-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> moves slightly </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">AND</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Motion-Width" styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Motion-Width</link><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> increases a small amount. </text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">You </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="color:#ff0000;" translate="true">must</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> use the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Segment-Editor" styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment-Editor</link><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> to edit the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-SegmentEditor-Segment-Width" styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Segment-Width</link><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> of the segments to make the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Motion-Width</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> = 360 again.</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
